snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Rogue Trader – Official Release Date Trailer
snippet.description: Check out the new release date trailer for Warhammer 40,000: Rogue Trader, the upcoming isometric cRPG from Owlcat Games set in the Warhammer 40,000 universe that will be released on December 7, 2023 for PC – and now also confirmed for PS5, Xbox Series X|S, and Mac.
